{
  "text": "41, [CITATION_1] However, systematic study of its interactions has been challenging due to its large size (necessitating the use of cDNA fragments instead of full-length cDNA) and to the difficulty in distinguishing specific from nonspecific proteins in the absence of quantitative methods.",
